Package: faissR
Type: Package
Title: Fast Native Nearest Neighbours, Graphs, kNN Models, and k-means
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Stefano",
    family = "Caccia",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "tkcaccia@gmail.com")
Author: Stefano Caccia [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Stefano Caccia <tkcaccia@gmail.com>
Description: Native nearest-neighbour search, graph construction, k-nearest
    neighbour prediction, and k-means helpers for large dimensionality
    reduction workflows. The package provides exact CPU reference search,
    optional FAISS CPU/GPU indexes, optional RAPIDS cuVS CUDA indexes, and a
    CRAN-friendly RcppHNSW fallback when optional system libraries are absent.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/tkcaccia/faissR
BugReports: https://github.com/tkcaccia/faissR/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    Rcpp
Suggests:
    igraph,
    RcppHNSW,
    testthat
LinkingTo:
    Rcpp
SystemRequirements: C++17, Fortran, optional FAISS C++ library for backend = "faiss", optional RAPIDS cuVS library for backend = "cuda_cuvs", optional CUDA toolkit for CUDA KNN backends, Metal framework on macOS for optional native Metal candidate kernels
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
Config/testthat/edition: 3
